{"tid":1442520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報紙:\"內地禁黑T運港 查封製衣廠\"","createTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T23:05:56.000Z","uid":302888,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9117cef198c036498bd1ded726b45a9428772cf","tid":1442520,"uid":302888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"沒字的黑T都一律不運怕人地印字上去"},{"pid":"ab721d714a4d5f22d1939dd40de8f9d59ba3c80c","tid":1442520,"uid":41245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=3685a0aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">45,061</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 11:42）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本識 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"49f57143f69d3a575958dc697b0f18dce2c41471","tid":1442520,"uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"UNIQLO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1472a058a42391330903c0c5b5652d1d0244a52b","tid":1442520,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用不推文功能</span>"},{"pid":"26bf9aecb066e75e7386fba053932b12a3143a7c","tid":1442520,"uid":216789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c6f7b0adc2be5389add21fdd4d3be9b9cf6995fe","tid":1442520,"uid":133534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo GU買到你窮啦"},{"pid":"2042486e5ec0722ffa059e3514a50aea40fa842d","tid":1442520,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"黑色底衫最平"},{"pid":"6253d72db62961598a293612cecb0e5c1af4ab1e","tid":1442520,"uid":2656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"其實啲大牌子好多都轉哂東南亞做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bb6ad345647a7fed23b89e2d01215d13386c12","tid":1442520,"uid":2656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"其實啲大牌子好多都轉哂東南亞做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39384dead6b08ca1bde3c2eea68cd50f0653884b","tid":1442520,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"一個14億人大國驚件黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d84a57d8cf6368e0d98caf2bf62a09af